description: Boyish, fit Ty Michell is having an affair with slender, cute Zach Country, his property owner’s husband, and he’s been feeling guilty about it. He tried to call it off, but Zach convinces him that everything will work out just fine, and no one will find out. They head off to shower together unaware that his wife is about to enter with the plumber!
title: Tricky Tricks Part 3
